hadiths[56]{hadithnumber,text}:
4342,"Leis ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-abi Hasma aur Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Sahal-bin-Zaid aur muhayyisa-bin-Masood-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) (Madina se) nikley yahan tak ke jab khaibar mein pahunchey to wahan kisi jagah alag-alag ho gaey. phir (ye hota hai ke) achanak muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) , Abdullah-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) ko maqtool patey hain. unhon-ne usey dafn kiya, phir wo khud , huwayyesa-bin-Masood aur) maqtool ka haqiqi bhai ( Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. wo ( Abdur-Rehman ( sabse kam Umr the, chunanche Abdur-Rehman apne donon sathiyon se pahley baat karne lage to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : badey ko uska maqam do, yani umr mein badey ko , to wo khamosh ho gaya, iske donon sathiyon ne baat ki aur unke sath usne bhi baat ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Abdullah-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) ke qatl ki baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : kya tum pachaas qasmein khaao gey , phir apne sathi (ke badley khoon baha ). padhi. ya ( farmaya :) badley mein apne qaatil (se diyat ya qisaas leney). padhi. ke haqdaar bano-gey? unhon-ne jawab diya : ham qasmein kaisey khaaein jabke ham ne dekha nahi ? aap ne farmaya : to yahood pachaas qasmein kha kar tumhen (unke khilaf tumharey mutaalbey ke haq se) alag kar dengey unhon-ne kaha : ham kaafir logon ki qasmein kyon kar qabool karein? jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye surate-haal dekhi aap ne (apni taraf se) uski diyat ada ki."
4343,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se, unhon-ne Sahal-bin-abi-hasma aur Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke muhayyisa-bin-Masood aur Abdullah-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar ki taraf gaey aur) wahan ( kisi nakhlistaan mein alag-alag ho gaey, Abdullah-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) ko qatl kar diya gaya to un logon ne yahood par ilzam Aaiz kiya, chunanche unke bhai Abdur-Rehman aur do huwayyisa aur muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne bhai ke mamley mein baat ki, wo un sab mein kam Umr they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : badey ko bada banao ya farmaya : sabse bada ( baat ke) shuruat kare. un donon ne apne sathi ke mamley mein guftgu ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se pachaas aadmi unmein se aik aadmi par qasmein khaaengey to wo apni rassi samet (jis mein wo bandhaa hoga ( tumharey hawale kar diya jaeyga? unhon-ne kaha : ye aisa mamla hai jo ham ne dekha nahi, ham kaisey Halaf uthayen? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to yahood apne pachaas aadmiyon ki qasmon se tum ko) tumharey da'wey ke haq se) alag kar dengey. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! (wo to ( kaafir log hain. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki diyat apni taraf se ada kar di. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aik din main unke baadey mein gaya to un oonton mein se aik ontni ne mujhey laat maari . Hammad ne kaha : ye ya uski tarah ( baat kahi .)"
4344,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se, unhon-ne Sahal-bin-abi-hasma (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki, aur unhon-ne apni hadis mein kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne paas se uski diyat de di aur unhon-ne apni hadis mein ye nahi kaha : mujhey aik ontni ne laat mar di."
4345,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se aur unhon-ne Saha-bin-abi-hasma (Raziallahu anhu) se unhi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4346,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein Abdullah-bin-Sahal-bin-Zaid Ansari aur muhayyisa-bin-Masood-bin-Zaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) , jinka talluq qabila banu-Haarisa se tha, khaibar ki taraf nikley, un dinon wahan suleh thi, aur wahan ke baashindey Yahudi they, to wo donon apni zarooriyaat ke peshe-nazar alag-alag ho gaey, baad iske Abdullah-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) qatl ho gaey aur khajoor ke taney ke ird-gird banaey gaey pani ke aik garhey mein maqtool haalat mein miley. unke sathi ne unhein dafn kiya, phir Madina aaey aur maqtool ke bhai Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sahal aur (chacha-zaad) muhayyisa aur huwayyesa (Raziallahu anhu) gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) aur unko qatl kiye janey ki surate-haal aur jagah batai. Bashir ka khayal hai aur wo un logon se hadis bayan kartey hain jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ko paya ke aap ne unse farmaya : kya tum pachaas qasmein kha kar apne qaatil. padhi. ya apne sathi . padhi. (se badla / diyat (ke haq daar bano-gey? unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! na ham ne dekha, na wahan maujood they. un ( Bashir (ka khayal hai ke aap ne farmaya : to yahood pachaas qasmein kha kar tumhen (apne da'wey ke haq se) alag kar dengey. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! ham kaafir logon ki qasmein kaisey qabool karein? Bashir ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni taraf se uski diyat ada farma di."
4347,"Hushaim ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se riwayat ki ke Ansar mein se banu- Harisa ka aik aadmi jisey Abdullah-bin-Sahal-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha aur uska chacha zaad bhai jisey muhayyisa-bin-Masood-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha, safar par rawaana huey, aur unhon-ne us qaul tak , Leis ki) hadis : 4342 ( ki tarah hadis bayan ki : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne paas se uski diyat ada farma di. Yahya ne kaha : mujhey Basheer-bin-Yasaar ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Sahal-bin-abi-hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : diyat ki un oontniyon mein se aik ontni ne mujhey baadey mein laat maari thi."
4348,"Saeed-bin-Ubaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Basheer-bin-Yasaar Ansari ne Sahal-bin-abi-hasma Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne unko bataya ke un (ke khandan ( mein se chand log khaibar ki taraf nikley aur wahan alag-alag ho gaey, baad iske unhon-ne apne aik aadmi ko qatl kiya hua paya. padhi. aur unhon-ne ( poori ( hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne na-pasand kiya ke uske khoon ko ray-gaan (bekar) qarar dein. chunanche aap ne sadqey ke oonton se sau oont uski diyat ada farma di."
4349,"abu-Laila-bin-Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sahal (bin-Zaid Ansari ( ne Sahal-bin-abi-hasma ( Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne unhein unki qaum ke badi umr ke logon se khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Sahal aur muhayyisa apni tangdasti ki bina par jo unhein laahiq ho gaee thi, ( tijarat wghaira ke liye) khaibar ki taraf nikley, baad iske muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur bataya ke Abdullah-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) qatl kar diye gaey hain. aur unhein kisi chashmey ya pani ke kachchey kuwein mein phenk diya gaya. chunanche wo yahood ke paas aaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum logon ne hi unhein qatl kiya hai. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham ne unhein qatl nahi kiya. phir wo aaey yahan tak ke apni qaum ke paas pahunchey aur unko ye baat batai , phir wo khud , unke bhai huwaiyyisa (Raziallahu anhu) , aur wo unse badey they, aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sahal (Raziallahu anhu)) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( aaey, muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu shuru ki aur wahi khaibar mein maujood they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : badey ko baat karne do, badey ko mauqa do aap ki murad umr (main badey ( se thi, to huweyyisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne baat ki, iske baad muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne baat ki, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya wo tumharey sathi ki diyat dein ya phir jang ka elaan karein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is silsiley mein unki taraf khat likha, to unhon-ne ( jawaaban ( likha : Allah ki qism ! ham ne unhein qatl nahi kiya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne huweyyisa, muhayyisa aur Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : kya tum qism kha kar apne sathi ke khoon (ka badla leney (ke haqdaar bano-gey? unhon-ne kaha : nahi. aap ne puchha : to tumharey samney yahood qasmein khaaein? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo musalman nahi hain. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne paas se uski diyat ada kar di, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sau oontniyan unki taraf rawana kin. yahan tak ke unke ghar ( baadey ( pahuncha di gain . Sehal ne kaha : unmein se aik surkh ontni ne mujhey laat maari thi."
4350,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne Ansar mein se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qasaama ko usi sura par bar-qaraar rakha jis par wo jahiliyat mein thi."
4351,ibne-Juraij ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur ye izafa kya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us ( qasaama (ke zariey Ansar ke logon ke beech aik maqtool ka faisla kiya jiska dawa unhon-ne yahood par kiya tha.
4352,Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke unhein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne Ansar ke kuchh logon se khabar di aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki jis tarah ibne-Juraij ki hadis hai.
4353,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Suhaib aur Humaid ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Uraina ke kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Madina aaey, unhein yahan ki aab aur hwa naa muwafiq lagi (aur unhein istisqaa ho gaya) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un (ke mutaalbey par unse ( farmaya : agar tum chahtey ho to sadqey ke oonton ke paas chaley jao aur unke doodh aur peshab ( jisey wo log , is tarah ki kaifiyat main apni sihat ka zaamin samajhtey they) piyo. unhon-ne aisey hi kiya aur sihat yaab ho gaey, phir unhon-ne charwaahon par hamla kar diya, unko qatl kar diya, Islam se murtad ho gaey. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) baitul-maal ke) oont haank kar ley gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aap ne ( kuchh logon ko) unke ta'aqub mein (peecha karne ke liye) rawaana kiya, unhein ( pakad kar) laya gaya to aap ne unke hath aur paon katwaa diye, unki aankhen phod dene ka hukm diya aur unhein siyah pattharon wali zamin mein chhod diya yahan tak ke) wahin ( mar gaey."
4354,"abu-Jafar Muhammad-bin-Sabaah aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, alfaz Abu-Bakar ke hain, kaha : hamein ibne-Ulaih ne Hujjaj-bin-abi-Usman se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Rajaa-Maula-abi-qulaaba ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke ukul (aur Uraina (ke aath (8) afraad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aap se Islam par bait ki, unhon-ne is sarzameen ki aab aur hwa ko na-muwaafiq paya aur unke jism kamzor ho gaey. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is baat ki shikayat ki to aap ne farmaya : tum hamarey charwaahey ke sath (jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke oont lekar usi mushtarka (saajha) charaagaah ki taraf ja raha tha jahan baitul-maal ke oont bhi chartey they : fatehul-baari 1/338 ( oonton mein kyon nahi chaley jatey taake unka peshab aur doodh piyo? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi ! chunanche wo nikley, unka peshab aur doodh piyaa aur sihat yaab ho gaey. phir unhon-ne (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) charwaahey ko qatl kiya aur oont bhi bhagaa le gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi to aap ne unke peechhey (eik dasta ( rawaana kiya, unhein pakad liya gaya aur (Madina mein) laya gaya to aap ne unke barey mein (Quraan ki saza par amal kartey huey) hukm diya, is par unke hath paon kaat diye gaey, unki aankhen garm salaakhon se phod di gain , phir unhein dhoop mein phenk diya gaya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey. ibne-Sabaah ne apni riwayat mein alfaaz mein kuch fer badal hai.( mana wahi hai.)"
4355,"Ayub ne abu-Qilaba ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Rajaa se riwayat ki, kaha : abu-Qilaba ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ukul ya Uraina ke kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Madina mein unhein istisqaa ki bimari laahiq ho gaee. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein doodh wali oontniyon ka hukm diya (ke unke liye khas kar di jayen (aur unse kaha ke unke peshab aur doodh piein. padhi. aagey Hujjaj-bin-abi-Usman ki hadis ke ham mana hai. aur kaha : unki aankhen garm salaakhon se phod di gain aur unhein siyah pattharon wali zamin ( Harra ( mein phenk diya gaya, wo pani maangtey they, to unhein nahi pilaya jata tha."
4356,"Ibne-Aun ne kaha : hamein abu-Rajaa-Maula-abi-qulaaba ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez ke peechhey betha tha to unhon-ne logon se kaha : tum qasaama ke barey mein kya kehtey ho? anbasaa ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne is-is tarah hadis bayan ki hai. is par maine kaha : mujhey bhi Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke kuchh log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. padhi. aur unhon-ne Ayub aur Hajjaj ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki. abu-Qilaba ne kaha : jab main farigh hua to anbasaa ne Subhan-Allah kaha ( tajjub ka izhar kya ). abu-Qilaba ne kaha : is par maine kaha : aey anbasaa ! kya tum mujh par) jhoot bolney ka ( ilzam lagaatey ho? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, hamein bhi Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah hadis bayan ki hai. aey ahale-Sham (Syria) ! jab tak tum mein ye ya un jaisey log maujood hain, tum hamesha bhalai se rahogey."
4357,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Qilaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ( qabila ( ukul ke aath (8) afraad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. padhi. aagey unhi ki hadis ki tarah hai aur unhon-ne hadis mein ye alfaz zayed bayan kiye : aur aap ne ( khoon rokney ke liye) unhein dagh nahi diya. (is tarah wo jaldi maut ke munh mein chaley gaey.)"
4358,"Muawiya-bin-Qurra ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Uraina ke kuchh afraad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey. wo musalman huey aur aap ki bait ki aur Madina mein mom . padhi. jo barsaam (phephdon ki jhilli ki sujan ka doosra naam) hai. ki wabaa phaili hui thi, phir unhi ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur mazeed kaha : aap ke paas Ansar ke taqriban bees naujawaan hazir they, aap ne unhein unki taraf rawaana kiya aur aap ne unke sath aik khoji bhi rawaana kiya jo unke paon ke nuqoosh (naqsh) ki nishaandehi karta tha."
4359,"Hammam aur Saeed ne Qatada ke hawale se Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, Hammam ki hadis mein hai : ureina ka aik giroh Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur Saeed ki hadis mein hai : ukul aur Uraina ka ( giroh aaya ( . padhi. aagey unhi ki hadis ki tarah hai."
4360,"Sulaiman Taimi ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( lohey ki salaakhon se) un logon ki aankhen phodney ka hukm diya kyonke unhon-ne bhi charwaahon ki aankhen phodi thin. (ye iqdaam (karwai), intiqaam ke qanoon ke mutabiq tha.)"
4361,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hisham-bin-Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik Yahudi ne aik ladki ko uske zewaraat ( hasil karne) ki khaatir mar daala , us ne usey patthar se qatl kiya, kaha : wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laai gaee aur is mein zindagi ki ramaq maujood thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik Yahudi ka naam letey huey) us se puchha : kya tujhey falan ne maara hai? us ne apne sar se nahi ka ishara kiya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se dusri baar ( doosra naam letey huey) puchha : to usne apne sar se nahi ka ishara kiya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se ( tesraa naam letey huey) teesri baar puchha : to usne kaha : haan , aur apne sar se ishara kiya, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ( mulawwis Yahudi ko iske iqrar ke ba'd, hadis : 4365 ( do pattharon ke darmyan qatl karwaa diya."
4362,Khalid-bin-Haaris aur ibne-Idrees donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki aur ibne-Idrees ki hadis mein hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska sar do pattharon ke darmyan kuchalwaa dala. (is tarah bhari patthar maara gaya ke uska sar kuchlaa gaya.)
4363,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein Mamar ne Ayub se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke yahood ke aik aadmi ne Ansar ki aik ladki ko uske zewaraat ki khaatir qatl kar diya, phir usey kuwein mein phenk diya, us ne iska sar patthar se kuchal diya tha. usey pakad liya gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kiya gaya to aap ne usey mar janey tak patthar maarney ka hukm diya, chunanche usey patthar maarey gaey yahan tak ke wo mar gaya."
4364,ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Mamar ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4365,"Qatada ne hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke aik ladki ka sar do pattharon ke darmyan kuchlaa hua mila to logon ne us se puchha : tumharey sath ye kis ne kya? falan ne ? falan ne ? yahan tak ke unhon-ne khas (usi) Yahudi ka zikr kiya to usne apne sar se ishara kiya. Yahudi ko pakda gaya to usne aetraaf kiya, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke uska sar patthar se kuchal diya jaey."
4366,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne zuraarah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Yala-bin-muniya (Raziallahu anhu) ya ibne-Umayya aik aadmi se lad padey to unmein se aik ne doosrey (ke hath) mein daant gaad diye, us ne iske munh se apna hath kheenchaa aur iska samney wala aik daant nikal diya. ibne- Musanna ne kaha : samney waley do daant . padhi. phir wo donon jhagdaa lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mein se koi (doosrey ko) is tarah (daant) kaat'taa hai jaisey saand kaat'taa hai? uski koi diyat nahi hai."
4367,"Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey ne Yala (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4368,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne doosrey ki kalaai ko daanton se kaataa, us ne usey kheenchaa to us ( kaatney waale) ka samney wala daant gir gaya. ye muqaddima Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kiya gaya to aap ne us (nuqsan) ko rayegaan (bekar) qarar diya aur farmaya : kya tum iska gosht khana chahtey they."
4369,"Budail ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se aur unhon-ne safwaan-bin-Yala se riwayat ki ke Yala-bin-muniya (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik mulaazim tha kisi aadmi ne uski kalaai ko daanton se kaataa , us ne usey kheenchaa to uska samney wala daant gir gaya. mamla Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak laya gaya to aap ne usey rayegaan (bekar) qarar diya aur farmaya : tum chahtey they ke usey ( uski kalaai ko is tarah) chabaa dalo jis tarah saand chabaataa hai."
4370,"Muhammad-bin-Sirin ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne doosrey aadmi ke hath ko daanton se kaataa , us ne apna hath kheenchaa to uska samney wala aik ya do daant gir gaey. is par us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se faryaad ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mujh se kya kehtey ho? tum mujhey ye kehtey ho ke main usey ye kahun : wo apna hath tumharey munh mein de aur tum is tarah usey chabaao jis tarah saand chabaataa hai? tum bhi apna hath (iske munh ki taraf ( badhaao yahan tak ke wo usey kaatney lagey, phir tum usey kheench lenaa."
4371,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Ata ne safwaan-bin-Yala-bin-muniya se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik aadmi hazir hua aur us ne kisi doosrey aadmi ke hath par daanton se kaataa tha, us ne apna hath kheenchaa to us , yani jisne kaataa tha, ke samney waley do daant nikal gaey. kaha : to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey rayegaan (bekar) qarar diya aur farmaya : tum ye chahtey they ke usey is tarah chabaao jis tarah saand chabaataa hai?"
4372,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey safwaan-bin-Yala-bin-Umayya ne apne walid se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Tabook mein shirkat ki, kaha : aur Hazrat Yala (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : wo jang mere nazdeek mera sabse qaabile-bharosa amal hai. Ata ne kaha : Safwan ne kaha : Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mera aik mulaazim tha, wo kisi insan se lad padaa to unmein se aik ne doosrey ke hath ko daanton se kaataa. padhi. kaha : mujhey Safwan ne bataya tha ke unmein se kis ne doosrey ko daanton se kaataa tha. padhi. jiska hath kaataa ja raha tha us ne apna hath kaatney waley ke munh se kheenchaa to uske samney waley do daanton mein se aik nikal diya, is par wo donon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap ne uske daant (ke nuqsan) ko rayegaan (bekar) qarar diya."
4373,Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
4374,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke rube' (Raziallahu anhu)) binte-nazar-bin-zamzam ( ki behan , Umme- Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kisi insan ko zakhmi kiya ( unhon-ne aik ladki ko thappad mar kar uska daant tod diya, sahi Bukhari ( to wo muqaddima lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qisaas ! qisaas ! to umme-rube' (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! kya falan aurat se qisaas liya jaeyga? Allah ki qism ! us se qisaas nahi liya jaeyga. is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! aey Umme- Rabe ! qisaas Allah ki kitab (ka hissey ( hai. unhon-ne kaha : nahi, Allah ki qism ! us se kabhi qisaas nahi liya jaeyga. ( Allah Taala apne Fazal se aisa nahi honey dega.) kaha : wo musalsal usi baat par (dati) rahein yahan tak ke wo log diyat par razi ho gaey. to is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke bandon mein se kuchh aisey hain ke agar wo Allah par qism khaaein to wo zaroor usey sachcha kar deta hai."
4375,"Hafs-bin-Ghiyas , abu-Muawia aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Murra se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi musalman ka, jo gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi haqiqi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun, khoon halal nahi, magar teen mein se kisi aik sura mein) halal hai) : shadi shuda zina karne waalaa, jaan ke badley mein jaan ( qisaas ki sura mein) aur apne Deen ko chhod kar jamat se alag ho janey wala."
4376,"Abdullah-bin-Numair , Sufiyan ( ibne-Uena (aur Esa-bin-Yonus sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4377,"Sufiyan ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Murra se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey darmyan ( Khattab ke liye) khadey huey aur farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi haqiqi maabood nahi ! kisi musalman aadmi ka khoon , jo gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun, halal nahi siwaey teen insanon ke : Islam ko chhodney wala jo jamat se alag honey wala ya jamat ko chhodney wala ho, shadi shuda zaani aur jaan ke badley jaan. (qisaas mein qatl honey wala.) Aamash ne kaha : maine ye hadis Ibrahim ko bayan ki to unhon-ne mujhey Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4378,Sheban ne Aamash se (pichhli ( donon sanadon ke sath Sufiyan ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki aur unhon-ne hadis mein aap ka farman is zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi maabood nahi ! bayan nahi kiya.
4379,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Murra se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi zi Rooh (insan) ko zulm se qatl nahi kiya ja sakta magar uske khoon ( gunah (ka aik hissey Adam ke pahley betey par padta hai. kyonke wahi sabse pahlaa shakhs tha jisne qatl ka tariqa nikala."
4380,"Jareer, Esa-bin-Yonus aur Sufiyan sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Jarir aur Esa-bin-Yonus ki hadis mein hai : kyonke us ne qatl ka tariqa nikala tha. un donon ne awwal ka lafz bayan nahi kiya."
4381,"Abda-bin-Sulaiman aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din logon ke beech sabse pahley jo faisley kiye jaeinge wo khoon ke barey mein hongey."
4382,"Muaaz-bin-Muaaz , Khalid-bin-Haaris , Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur ibne-abi-Adi sab ne Shoba se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta unmein se kuchh ne Shoba se riwayat kartey huey ( يقضى (ka lafz kaha aur kuchh ne ( يحكم بين Naas ( kaha. ( mana wahi hai.)"
4383,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Yahya-bin-Habib-haarisi donon ke alfaz qareeb-qareeb hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne ibne-abi-bakra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah zamana ghoom kar apni usi haalat par aa gaya hai (jo us din tha) jis din Allah ne aasmanon aur zamin ko paida kiya tha. saal ke baara mahiney hain. unmein se char hurmat waley hain. teen lagaataar hain : zul-Qada , zul-hijja aur mohrram aur (inke ilawa) rajab jo muzer ka mahina hai, ( jiski hurmat ka qabila muzer qaail hai) jo jumadi aur Shoban ke darmyan hai. iske baad aap ne puchha : (aaj) ye kon sa mahina hai? ham ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada jaanney waley hain. kaha : aap khamosh ho gaey yahan tak ke ham ne khayal kiya ke aap isey uske ( Maruf ( naam ke bajaey koi aur naam dengey. ( phir (aap ne farmaya : kya ye zul-hijja nahi hai? ham ne jawab diya : kyon nahi ! ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye kon sa Shahar hai? ham ne jawab diya : Allah aur uska rasool sabse badh kar jaanney waley hain. kaha : aap khamosh rahe yahan tak ke ham ne khayal kiya ke aap uske ( Maruf ( naam se hat kar usey koi aur naam dengey, (phir) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya ye al-balda (hurmat wala Shahar) nahi? ham ne jawab diya : kyon nahi ! (phir) aap ne puchha : ye kon sa din hai? ham ne jawab diya : Allah aur uska rasool sabse badh kar jaanney waley hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha : kya ye din qurbani ka din nahi hai? ham ne jawab diya : kyon nahi, Allah ke rasool ! ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah tumharey khoon , tumharey maal . padhi. Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( ne kaha : mera khayal hai, unhon-ne kaha : aur tumhari izzat tumharey liye isi tarah hurmat waley hain jis tarah is mahiney mein, is Shahar main tumhara ye din hurmat wala hai, aur an-qareeb tum apne rab se milo gey aur wo tum se tumharey amal ke barey mein poochhega. tum mere baad hargiz dobara gumrah na ho jana ke aik doosrey ki gardanein maarney lago, suno ! jo shakhs yahan maujood hai wo us shakhs tak ye paigham pahuncha de jo yahan maujood nahi, mumkin hai jis ko ye paigham pahunchaya jaey wo usey us aadmi se zyada yad rakhney wala ho jisne usey (khud mujh se) suna hai. phir farmaya : suno ! kya maine ( Allah ka paigham ( theek taur par pahuncha diya hai? ibne-Habib ne apni riwayat mein muzer ka rajab kaha : aur Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein (tum mere baad hargiz dobara ke bajaey) mere baad dobara (takeed ke baghair) hai."
4384,"Yazeed-bin-Zuree ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Aun ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi bakra se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab wo din tha, (jiska aagey zikr hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne oont par baithey aur aik insan ne uski lagaam pakad li to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke ye kon sa din hai? logon ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada jaanney waley hain. yahan tak ke ham ne khayal kiya ke aap iske naam ke siwa usey koi aur naam dengey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya ye qurbani ka din nahi ? ham ne kaha : kyon nahi, Allah ke rasool ! farmaya : ye kon sa mahina hai? ham ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada jaanney waley hain, farmaya : kya ye zul-hijja nahi ? ham ne kaha : kyon nahi, Allah ke rasool ! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye kon sa Shahar hai? ham ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada jaanney waley hain. kaha : ham ne khayal kiya ke aap iske (Maruf) naam ke siwa usey koi aur naam dengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya ye al-balda (hurmat wala Shahar) nahi ? ham ne kaha : kyon nahi, Allah ke rasool ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah tumharey khoon , tumharey maal aur tumhari namus ( izzatein ( tumharey liye isi tarah hurmat waley hain jis tarah is Shahar mein, is mahiney main tumhara ye din hurmat wala hai. yahan maujood shakhs ghair maujood ko ye paigham pahuncha de. kaha : phir aap do chitkabrey ( safaid aur siyah ( mendhon ki taraf mudey , unhein zabah kiya aur bakriyon ke galley ki taraf (aaey) aur unhein hamarey darmyan taqseem farmaya."
4385,"Hammad-bin-Mas-ada ne hamein Ibne-Aun se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( ne kaha : Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra ne apne walid se riwayat kartey huey kaha : jab wo din tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne oont par baithey. kaha : aur aik aadmi ne uski baag . padhi. ya kaha : lagaam . padhi. thaam li. padhi. aagey Yazeed-bin-Zuree ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4386,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne kaha : hamein Qurra-bin-Khalid ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Sirin ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra se aur aik aur aadmi se, jo mere khayal mein Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra se afzal hai, hadis bayan ki, neez (isi ke saath) abu-Aamir abdul-Malik-bin-Amr ne kaha : hamein Qurra ne Yahya-bin-Saeed ki) mazkura (uper zikr) (sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. padhi. aur unhon ( abu-Aamir ( ne is aadmi ka naam Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman bataya (ye Basra ke faqeeh tareen (samajhdar) rawi hain) . padhi. unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein qurbani ke din khutba diya aur puchha : ye kon sa din hai? aur unhon (Qurra) ne Ibne-Aun ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne izzat aur nam ka tazkira nahi kiya aur na hi : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) do mendhon ki taraf mudey aur uske baad wala hissey bayan kiya. unhon-ne (apni ( hadis mein kaha : jaisey tumharey is Shahar mein, tumharey is mahiney main tumhara ye din us waqt tak qaabile ehtiraam hai jab tum apne rab se milo gey. suno ! kya maine ( Allah ka paigham ( pahuncha diya? logon ne kaha : ji haan ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! gawah rehna."
4387,"Samak-bin-Harab ne Alqama bin Waail se hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne unhein hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath betha hua tha ke aik shakhs doosrey ko mendhi ki tarah bani hui chamdey ki rassi se kheenchtey huey laya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! us ne mere bhai ko qatl kya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya tum ne usey qatl kya hai? to us (kheenchney waale) ne kaha : agar us ne aetraaf na kya to main iske khilaf shahadat pesh karunga. usne kaha : ji haan, maine usey qatl kya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : tum ne usey kaisey qatl kiya? usne kaha : main aur wo aik darakht se patey jhaad rahe they, usne mujhey gali di aur ghussa dilaya to maine kulhaadi se iske sar ki aik taraf maara aur usey qatl kar diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : kya tumharey paas koi cheez hai jo tum apni taraf se (bataur fidya) ada kar sako? usne kaha : mere paas to odhney ki chadar aur kulhaadi ke siwa aur koi maal nahi hai. aap ne puchha : tum samajhtey ho ke tumhari qaum (tumhari taraf se diyat ada karke) tumhen khareed legi? usne kaha : main apni qaum ke nazdeek us se haqeer tar hun. aap ne us (wali) ki taraf rassa phainktey huey farmaya : jisey sath laey they usey pakad lo. wo aadmi usey lekar chal pada. jab us ne rukh phera to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar us aadmi ne usey qatl kar diya to wo bhi usi jaisa hai. is par wo shakhs wapas hua aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool! mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai : agar us ne usey qatl kar diya to wo bhi usi jaisa hai halanke maine usey aap ke hukm se pakda hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum nahi chahtey ke wo tumharey aur tumharey sathi (bhai) donon ke gunah ko (apne uper) lekar lautey? usne kaha : Allah ke Nabi! ghaaliban us ne kaha, padhi. kyon nahi ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to yaqinan wo (qaatil) yahi karega. kaha : is par us ne rassa phainkaa aur uska rasta chhod diya."
4388,"Ismail bin Salim ne Alqama bin Waail se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aadmi ko laya gaya jisne kisi shakhs ko qatl kya tha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maqtool ke wali ko us se qisaas leney ka haq diya, wo usey lekar chala jabke uski gardan mein chamdey ka aik mendhi numa rassa tha jisey wo kheench raha tha, jab us ne pusht pheri to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qaatil aur maqtool (donon) aag mein hain. (ye sun kar) aik aadmi us (wali) ke paas aaya aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat batai to usne usey chhod diya. Ismail bin Salim ne kaha : maine ye hadis Habib bin Sabit se bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ibne- Ashwa ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (wali) se mutalba kya tha ke usey maaf kar de to usne inkar kar diya tha."
4389,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke (qabeela) huzail ki 2 aurton mein se aik ne dusri ko (patthar) maara aur uske pet ke bachchey ko gira diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein aik ghulam , mard ya aurat ( bataur taawaan ( dene ka faisla farmaya."
4390,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Lahyaan (jo qabila huzail ki shaakh hai) ki aik aurat ke pet ke bachchey ke barey mein, jo murda zaaye hua tha, aik ghulam ya londi diye janey ka faisla kya, phir wo aurat ( bhi) faut ho gaee jiske khilaf aap ne ghulam ( bataur diyat dene) ka faisla kya tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke uski wiraasat (jo bhi hai) iske beton aur shauhar ke liye hai aur (uski taraf se) diyat (ki adaaeygi) uske bap ki taraf se mard rishte-daaron par hai."
4391,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Huzail ki 2 auratein aapas mein lad padin to unmein se aik ne dusri ko patthar de maara aur usey qatl kar diya aur us bachchey ko bhi jo iske pet mein tha, chunanche wo jhagda lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke janeen ki diyat aik ghulam, mard ya aurat hai aur aap ne faisla kya ke aurat ki diyat us ( qaatila (ke aaqila ke zimmey hai aur iska waaris iske betey aur unke sath maujood doosrey haqdaaron ko banaya. is par Hamal bin naabgha hazli ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! main iska taawaan kaisey dun jisne na piya, na khaya, na bola, na awaz nikaali, aisa (khoon) to rayegaan hota hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye to kaahinon ke bhaiyon mein se hai. uski saja' (qaafiya daar kalam) ki wjah se, jo usney jodi thi."
4392,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : 2 auratein aapas mein lad padin. padhi. aur poorey qissey samet hadis bayan ki aur ye zikr nahi kya : aap ne iske betey aur uske sath maujood doosrey haqdaaron ko iska waaris banaya aur kaha : is par aik kehney waley ne kaha : ham kaisey diyat dein? aur unhon-ne hamal bin Malik ka naam nahi liya."
4393,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Ubaid bin Nazeela Khuzai se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aurat ne apni sautan ko jabke wo haamla thi, khema ki lakdi (aur patthar , hadis : 4389 ( se maara aur qatl kar diya. kaha : aur unmein se aik qabila banu- Lahyaan se thi. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qatl honey wali ki diyat qatl karne wali ke usba (jaddi rishtedar mardon ( par dali aur pet ke bachchey ka taawaan jo uske pet mein tha, aik ghulam muqarrar farmaya, is par qatl karne wali ke usba (jaddi mard rishte-daaron) mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : kya ham iska taawaan dengey jisne khaya na piya aur na awaz nikaali, aisa (khoon) to rayegaan hota hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya badduon ki saja' (qaafiya bandi ( jaisi saja' hai? kaha : aur aap ne diyat un (jaddi mard rishte-daaron) par dali ."
4394,"Mufazzal ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Ubaid bin Nazeela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aurat ne apni sautan ko khemey ki lakdi se qatl kar diya, us ( mamley ( ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya to aap ne us aurat ke aaqila par diyat Aaiz honey ka faisla farmaya aur chunkey wo haamla ( bhi) thi to aap ne pet ke bachchey ke badley mein aik ghulam ( bataur taawaan diye janey (ka faisla kya, is par iske usba (jaddi mard rishte-daaron ( mein se kisi ne kaha : kya ham uski diyat dein jisne na khaya, na piyaa, na cheekha, na chillaya, is tarah ka ( khoon ( to rayegaan hota hai, kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya badduon ki saja' jaisi saja' hai?"
4395,Sufiyan ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath Jarir aur Mufazzal ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki.
4396,"Shoba ne Mansoor se unhi ki (pichhli) sanadon ke sath mukammal qissey samet hadis riwayat ki, albatta usmein hai is aurat ka hamal saaqit ho gaya, ye muqaddima Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kya gaya to aap ne usmein (pet ke bachchey ke badley) aik ghulam ya londi dene ka faisla farmaya aur ye diyat un logon par dali jo aurat ke wali they. unhon-ne hadis mein aurat ki diyat ka zikr nahi kya."
4397,"Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon se aurat ke pet ka bachcha zaaye karne (ki diyat (ke barey mein mashwara kya to Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir tha, aap ne usmein aik ghulam, mard ya aurat dene ka faisla farmaya tha. kaha : to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere paas aisa aadmi lao jo tumharey sath (is baat ki) gawahi de. kaha : to Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke liye gawahi di."
